data.name: Classic French Toast
data.quickTastyDescription: Deliciously golden brown French toast, perfect for breakfast or brunch!
detailedCookingInstructions: In a bowl, whisk together eggs, milk, and vanilla extract until well combined.
Heat a non-stick skillet over medium heat and add butter.
Dip each slice of bread into the egg mixture, ensuring both sides are well coated.
Place the soaked bread slices onto the skillet and cook until golden brown on both sides, about 2-3 minutes per side.
Serve hot, drizzled with maple syrup and dusted with powdered sugar if desired.
data.detailedName: Classic French Toast with Maple Syrup
data.modifiersForBase: Classic style with vanilla and maple syrup
